title: How to configure the H350L router function
answer:
1） Connect PC to H350L via Ethernet cable or Wi-Fi, visit [http://192.168.1.1](http://192.168.1.1/) on browser.

2） Log on the WebUI, the default password is **admin.**

**Notes: the WEBUI default PASSWORD is display on the back on back**

3） Follow the Configuration Guide to complete the settings while log on the first time 

4） For more details about settings, please click **help**.
